# b1_release.shot — same fall, but release 'right' while still in the
# air so the anim transitions to STAND on landing and the anchor fires.
# If THIS settles cleanly while the previous test stays crumpled, the
# bug is "anchor disabled during ANIM_RUN".

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/b1_release
mouse  900 360

at  20 shot pre_t020
at  30 press right
at  85 release right        # released while mid-air

burst land from 90 to 130 every 1
burst settled from 140 to 200 every 5

at 220 end
